name: A Place To Start
description: "A Place To Start" is special. It was made in tandem with a music playlist, which only very few people will ever hear.   - // -   When doesn't matter - but it was a time of great turmoil. I was at a point in my life when I realised that my inner romantic-idealist was dying, yet still trying very hard to stay alive... While, at the same time, my inner cynic and I were celebrating, finally getting to know each other better as I began to accept him as an important part of me.  - // -   The piece is meant to represent my own brain, in obvious turmoil, but also full of brightly flaring moments of recognition that things were changing; that the future held countless possibilities; that sometimes there's just no good choice and someone always gets hurt; but also that no matter the outcome, any moment in time can be a great place to start...
